-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">PMS 175C</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/1/9125485AB07D5AFA7D5E87D9D07B655C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">40/PMS Color Match</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">PMS Color Match</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$40.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Optional Blank Vinyl Pouch</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Includes cost to fold and insert cloth inside pouch. Cloths are hand inserted into pouch.</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">MFP-VinylPouch</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Proof Options</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">F/E Proof</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Fax/Email Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Fax/Email Proof Charge: 7.50 (G)&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Add 2 days to production time&lt;/strong&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$7.50 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Spec Sample</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Speculative Sample</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">$25 (G), plus setup charges, cost of the item ,and cost of any additional color per unit running charges and freight charges. &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Production Time: 3-5 Days &lt;/strong&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$25.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Pre-Prod Proof</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Pre-Production Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">$45 (G), plus setup charges, cost of the item ,and cost of any additional color per unit running charges and freight charges. If any changes are made to the original artwork after receipt of the pre-production sample, then additional set-up charges will also be added to the invoice. &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Add 2-3 Days to production time.&lt;/strong&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$45.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — &quot;ONECLEANSCREEN&quot; 6&quot; X 6&quot; 100% Microfiber Recycled RPET Polyester Cleaning Cloth &amp; Screen Cleaner. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">5088</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>7 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">350</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}